(2254, 1, 'Alpine ICS-X8 App Link, Smart Phone, USB, Bluetooth', '<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>The Alpine ICS-X8 is the worlds first Double DIN touchscreen DVD mobile media product to take advantage of the MirrorLink standard and Nokia Car Mode, making it extremely convenient to use a Nokia smartphone and its applications in your car. Simply download Nokia Car Mode from the OVI store to add the great Nokia Drive and Nokia Music apps to your App Link Station. </p><br>\r\n<p>Those great features make it the worlds most advanced mobile information and entertainment centre, with a brilliant interface optimised for smartphones and apps. From sound quality and media support to navigation, everything is first-rate. </p><br>\r\n<p>To keep you entertained in the future, the Alpine ICS-X8 will stay up to date with support for new phones and apps from the Alpine website. </p><br>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Features</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><ul><li>7 inch WVGA High Resolution Display </li>\r\n<li>DVD/CD Player </li>\r\n<li>High Grade Audiophile Design </li>\r\n<li>Nokia Drive: Add free-of-charge navigation to your ICS-X8 </li>\r\n<li>Nokia Music: Makes Your Smartphone an Advanced Music Source </li>\r\n<li>Customisable Interface for a New Dimension of Usability </li>\r\n<li>Superior Sound Quality with Many Customisation Features </li>\r\n<li>Provides the Best iPhone/iPod Experience </li>\r\n<li>Built-in Bluetooth with New and Advanced Functions </li>\r\n<li>Unlimited Access to the Wide World of AV Media </li></ul><br>\r\n<p><b>Tuner </b></p><br>\r\n<ul><li>Memory Presets: Preset Stations (FM:18, MW:6, LW:6) </li>\r\n<li>Station Name Display </li>\r\n<li>Auto Preset Memory </li>\r\n<li>Seek Mode: Local / DX </li>\r\n<li>RDS </li>\r\n<li>RDS Functions: AF, TA, TP, PTY, News, EON, Radio Text </li></ul><br>\r\n<p><b>Bluetooth </b></p><br>\r\n<ul><li>Built-in BLUETOOTH Module </li>\r\n<li>Hands Free Calling: HFP (Hands-Free Profile) with compatible phones </li>\r\n<li>Streaming Music: A2DP (Advanced Audio Distribution Profile) with compatible devices </li>\r\n<li>Streaming Music Control: AVRCP (Audio/Video Remote Control Profile) ver.1.0, 1.3 and 1.4 compatible </li>\r\n<li>SSP (Simple Secure Pairing) supported </li>\r\n<li>Advanced BLUETOOTH Technology </li>\r\n<li>Phone Book Synchronization </li>\r\n<li>Phone Book Search: Percentage Search </li>\r\n<li>Short Cut Dialling: 3 Preset Memory </li>\r\n<li>Multiple Phone Number Registration: 5 Phone Number Registration Possibility </li>\r\n<li>Phone Book Label Display: General, Mobile, Home, Office, Other </li>\r\n<li>Auto Answer </li>\r\n<li>Call History Display: Dialled Calls, Unanswered Calls, Received Calls, Missed Calls </li>\r\n<li>Redial Function </li>\r\n<li>Speech Volume Level Adjustment for Outgoing and Incoming Volume </li>\r\n<li>GSM Signal Strength Indicator </li>\r\n<li>Cell-phone Battery Level Indicator </li>\r\n<li>Output Speaker Selection </li>\r\n<li>Firmware Updatable </li>\r\n<li>Microphone Included </li></ul><br>\r\n<p><b>Made for iPod / iPhone </b></p><br>\r\n<ul><li>Music & Video Playback Compatible </li>\r\n<li>Connection: USB Cable (KCU-461iV) Required </li>\r\n<li>Compatibility for iPod / iPhone: Made for iPod touch 4G/3G/2G/1G, iPod nano 6G/5G/4G/3G/2G/1G, iPod classic 160GB/120GB/80GB, iPod with video, iPhone 4, iPhone 3GS, iPhone 3G and iPhone </li>\r\n<li>Search Criteria: Playlists, Artists, Albums, Songs, Podcasts, Genres, Composers and Audiobooks </li>\r\n<li>Alphabet Search </li>\r\n<li>Percentage Search </li>\r\n<li>Direct Up/Down: Playlist, Artist, Album, Podcast, Genre and Composer </li>\r\n<li>Repeat </li>\r\n<li>M.I.X. (Shuffle) Play: Song, Album, All </li>\r\n<li>Artwork Display </li>\r\n<li>Cover Flow </li>\r\n<li>Battery Charging </li></ul><br>\r\n<p><b>Works with Nokia </b></p><br>\r\n<ul><li>Works with supported Nokia Phones: Mass Storage Mode Connection </li>\r\n<li>Micro USB Cable Included </li>\r\n<li>Music Playback: MP3, WMA, AAC </li>\r\n<li>File/Folder Name Search </li>\r\n<li>Tag Info Search </li>\r\n<li>Folder Up/Down Control </li>\r\n<li>Battery Charging </li>\r\n<li>MirrorLink </li>\r\n<li>Controllable Functions: Nokia Drive, Nokia Music </li>\r\n<li>Compatible Devices: Nokia 700/701/603 (with Symbian Belle) </li>\r\n<li>Connection: Micro USB Cable Included </li>\r\n<li>Battery Charging </li></ul><br>\r\n<p><b>Disc Player </b></p><br>\r\n<ul><li>Disc Type: DVD/CD Player </li>\r\n<li>Disc Playback Type: DVD-Video, DVDR/RW, CD, CD-R/RW </li>\r\n<li>Playable Format: MP3, WMA, AAC, DivX </li>\r\n<li>Repeat </li>\r\n<li>DVD Direct Menu Control </li>\r\n<li>M.I.X. Random Play </li>\r\n<li>CD Text Display </li>\r\n<li>CD Text Name Search </li>\r\n<li>Zero data Mute </li>\r\n<li>Digital Servo </li></ul><br>\r\n<p><b>USB Media Connection </b></p><br>\r\n<ul><li>USB Connection: USB Cable Included (2pcs) </li>\r\n<li>Music & Video Playback Compatible </li>\r\n<li>Playable Format: MP3, WMA, AAC, DivX (.avi, .divx) </li>\r\n<li>USB Class: Mass Storage Class </li>\r\n<li>File/Folder Name Search </li>\r\n<li>Tag Info Search </li>\r\n<li>Folder Up/Down Control </li></ul><br>\r\n<p><b>Sound Tuning </b></p><br>\r\n<ul><li>Subwoofer Level Adjustment </li>\r\n<li>Subwoofer Phase Select: 0/180 </li>\r\n<li>4-volt Pre Output (Front/Rear/Subwoofer): </li>\r\n<li>Equalizer: Flat, Pops, Rock, News, Jazz, Electrical Dance, Hip Hop, Easy Listening, Country, Classical </li>\r\n<li>9-band Parametric Equalizer </li>\r\n<li>Source Tone Memory </li>\r\n<li>MediaXpander </li>\r\n<li>Digital Time Correction </li>\r\n<li>Digital Crossover Setting </li>\r\n<li>Application Volume Level Setting </li></ul><br>\r\n<p><b>General</b> </p><br>\r\n<ul><li>Power Output: 4 x 50 W High Power Amplifier </li>\r\n<li>Display: 7 inch WVGA High Resolution Display </li>\r\n<li>Motorized Display Operation </li>\r\n<li>Control Type: Touch, Drag and Flick </li>\r\n<li>Illumination Buttons: 5 Colour (White, Blue, Green, Red, Amber) Selection </li>\r\n<li>Display Colour Setting: 4 Colour (Blue, Green, Red, Amber) Selection </li>\r\n<li>High Grade Audiophile Design </li>\r\n<li>PreOut: 3 PreOuts (4-volt) and 1 A/V AUX Output </li>\r\n<li>DAC: 24-Bit DAC </li>\r\n<li>AUX-In: 1 A/V AUX Output </li>\r\n<li>Steering Wheel Remote Control Ready </li>\r\n<li>OEM Sub-display Output </li>\r\n<li>Alpine Navigation Input (13-pin connector) </li>\r\n<li>Navigation Guidance Mix </li>\r\n<li>GPS Antenna Connection (for smartphone connection): GPS Signal Pass-through (KAE-100GPS required) </li>\r\n<li>Camera Connection: Alpine Direct Input Compatible </li>\r\n<li>Camera Angle Controls: Rear View, Panorama View, Corner View, Ground View </li>\r\n<li>Camera Guide Line Adjustment </li>\r\n<li>Visual EQ </li>\r\n<li>Live Contrast Adjustment </li>\r\n<li>Display Tuning Preset Memory </li>\r\n<li>User Interface Language: English, French, Spanish, German, Italian, Russian, Dutch, Portguese, Swedish, Finish, Norwegian </li>\r\n<li>Calendar/Clock Display </li>\r\n<li>Auto Dimmer </li>\r\n<li>Favorite Source Setting </li>\r\n<li>Anti-theft Security Code </li>\r\n<li>Firmware Updatable </li>\r\n<li>2DIN Size </li>\r\n<li>Power Antenna Lead </li>\r\n<li>Remote Turn-On </li></ul>\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Support</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc">\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>More Images</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc">\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>', '', '<a target="_blank" href="http://rover.ebay.com/rover/1/710-53481-19255-0/1?icep_ff3=9&pub=5575070011&toolid=10001&campid=5337621243&customid=&icep_uq=Alpine+ICS-X8&icep_sellerId=&icep_ex_kw=&icep_sortBy=12&icep_catId=&icep_minPrice=&icep_maxPrice=&ipn=psmain&icep_vectorid=229508&kwid=902099&mtid=824&kw=lg">&lt;img s