li>\n<li>20-850hz Impedance</li>\n<li>4ohm Mounting Depth</li>\n<li>168mm Mounting Diameter: 350mm</li>\n', ''),
(639, 1, 'Vibe BlackAir BA10 v3 1300W 10" Subwoofer', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>Bass is the rhythm of life and the new BlackAir subwoofer is the beat behind that rhythm. The eye catching subwoofer features a specially fabricated fibreglass composite cone which delivers bass with power and precision. The cone is partnered with a unique High Roll rubber edge surround which allows for exceptional excursion which is fully under control.\nThe all new magnet is significantly larger resulting in gains in both sound quality and power while the rubber boot protects the magnet and integrates with the basket, while the VIBE Angular Torsion basket has five vented arms which cradle the cone and allow the coil to breathe cool air.\nThe Alloy gasket signs off the BlackAir in true VIBE style - and is fully removable for the option of rear mounting.</p><br>\n<p>Add to all of this the fact that the BlackAir now comes with dual 2ohm voice coils and you have a subwoofer which not only looks fantastic but offers slamming bass even the most brutal of bass heads can appreciate.</p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>\n\n<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Features</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><ul><li>10" BlackAir Version3 subwoofer</li>\n<li>Speaker Size: 10" (275mm) </li>\n<li>RMS Power: 450W </li>\n<li>Peak Power: 1300W </li>\n<li>Minimum Input: 125W RMS </li>\n<li>Sensitivity: 89db </li>\n<li>Freq.Response: 20 - 1700 Hz </li>\n<li>Impendence: DUAL 2-OHM (can be wired into 4-ohm or 1-ohm load)</li>\n<li>Mounting Depth: 150mm</li>\n<li>Mounting Diameter: 285mm</li>\n<li>X-Max: 7.5mm </li>\n<li>Voice Coil: 2" aluminium 4 layer </li>\n<li>Magnet Material: Ferite </li>\n<li>Magnet Weight: 40oz </li>\n<li>Magnet Size: 140x 20mm </li>\n<li>Magnet Rating: Y25</li></ul>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>\n\n<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Support</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><a href="http://www.vibeaudio.co.uk/support/tsparameters/sub-blackair10.pdf" target="_blank"><img src="images/icons/pdf.png" align="left" style="vertical-align:middle"/>Instruction Manual</a><br>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>\n\n<newtab>\n<tabname><center>More Images</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p></p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/blackairsub10/', NULL, '', 62, '<br>\n<li>10" BlackAir Version3 subwoofer</li>\n<li>Speaker Size: 10" (275mm) </li>\n<li>RMS Power: 450W </li>\n<li>Peak Power: 1300W </li>\n', ''),
