(662, 1, 'Vibe Slick Bass Pack 1 12" Sub Amplifier Box Wiring Kit', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>Vibe are pleased to present the latest Slick Bass Pack. This package has the newly developed Vibe Slick A0 400W amplifier. The heat sink is super smooth and has elegant profiling and a rubberised finish. End caps terminate the profile whilst hiding wiring and connections.</p><br>\n<p>To partner the amp Vibe have created the totally unique 1200W SLR12 sealed enclosure with a 12" Slick subwoofer fitted as standard. The SLR enclosure has been tuned by the VIBE R&D department to ensure that it gets the ultimate sound out of the chosen woofer. The shape of the enclosure allows a smaller footprint taking up less space than conventional enclosures.</p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>\n\n<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Features</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><ul><li>Features:</li>\n<li>1 x Vibe Slick A0 400W Amplifier</li>\n<li>1 x Vibe SLR12 12" 1200W Subwoofer Box</li>\n<li>1 x Vibe Critical Link Wiring Kit</li>\n<li>2/1 channel amplifier</li>\n<li>Super Slick design with rubberised finish</li>\n<li>Twin end caps for stealth connections</li>\n<li>Soft turn on feature</li>\n<li>Optional bass boost remote control</li>\n<li>12db bass boost</li>\n<li>2 ohm stable</li>\n<li>Selectable HP/LP/Flat crossovers</li>\n<li>High quality surface mounted components</li>\n<li>Double sided PCB</li>\n<li>Preouts for linking additional amplifiers</li>\n<li>Lo-level and Hi-level inputs</li>\n<li>Built in relay protection</li>\n<li>Power @ 4 ohms 2 x 75 WRMS</li>\n<li>Power @ 2 Ohms 2 x 100 WRMS</li>\n<li>Power Bridged 1 x 200 WRMS</li>\n<li>Max Power: 400W</li>\n<li>Minimum speaker impedance 2 ohm</li>\n<li>THD Distortion 0.14 %</li>\n<li>IMD Distortion 0.1 %</li>\n<li>Input Sensitivity 200 mv - 6V</li>\n<li>Input Impedance 15 K</li>\n<li>Signal to Noise Ratio 93 dB</li>\n<li>Crossover range: 45 - 300Hz</li>\n<li>Bass Boost 0 dB -+12 dB</li>\n<li>Size H 65mm x W 380mm x D 245mm</li>\n<li>Height: 360mm</li>\n<li>Width: 400mm</li>\n<li>Bottom Depth: 400mm</li>\n<li>Driver: SLICK s12</li>\n<li>RMS Power: 400w</li>\n<li>Peak Power: 1200w</li>\n<li>VIBE N-wedge 2 enclosure design</li>\n<li>Heavy duty carpet with VIBE stitching and VIBE Rubber Crackle</li>\n<li>Sealed enclosure for extremely tight, punchy, fast bass.</li>\n<li>VIBE TP2 spring loaded terminal posts for easy and secure connection</li>\n<li>18mm MDF construction and braced for absolute rigidity.</li>\n<li>The extra rigid design improves sound by eliminating the power lost</li></ul>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>\n\n<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Support</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p></p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>\n\n<newtab>\n<tabname><center>More Images</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p></p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/slickpack1/', NULL, '', 106, '<br>\n<li>1 x Vibe Slick A0 400W Amplifier</li>\n<li>1 x Vibe SLR12 12" 1200W Subwoofer Box</li>\n<li>1 x Vibe Critical Link Wiring Kit</li>\n<li>2/1 channel amplifier</li>\n', ''),
(663, 1, 'Vibe Slick Pack 2 12" 800W Sub / Amp And 6x9 Package', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>Vibe are pleased to present the latest Slick System Pack. This package has the newly developed Vibe Slick A1 800W four channel amplifier. The heat sink is super smooth and has elegant profiling and a rubberised finish. End caps terminate the profile whilst hiding wiring and connections.</p><br>\n<p>To partner the amp Vibe have created the totally unique 1200W SLR12 sealed enclosure with a 12" Slick subwoofer fitted as standard. The SLR enclosure has been tuned by the VIBE R&D department to ensure that it gets the ultimate sound out of the chosen woofer. The shape of the enclosure allows a smaller footprint taking up less space than conventional enclosures.</p><br>\n<p>The system pack also includes a pair of Vibe Slick 3-Way 475W 6x9" speakers with stiffened IMPP cones and hard PU surrounds incorporating Fastbass technology.</p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>\n\n<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Features</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p><b>Features:</b></p><br>\n<ul><li>4 channel</li>\n<li>Height 65mm</li>\n<li>Width 380mm</li>\n<li>Depth 245mm</li>\n<li>RMS @ 4ohms stereo 4x75w</li>\n<li>RMS @ 2ohms stereo 4x100w</li>\n<li>RMS @ 4ohms mono 2x200w</li>\n<li>Max power watts 800w</li>\n<li>Frequency Response 20 Hz - 20Khz</li>\n<li>SNR 92db</li>\n<li>High/Low Pass Crossover 45 - 300Hz</li>\n</ul>\n<p><b>Subwoofer Enclosure SLR12:</b></p><br>\n<ul><li>Height 360mm</li>\n<li>Length 400mm</li>\n<li>Depth 400mm</li>\n<li>Driver Slick 12"</li>\n<li>RMS Power 400w</li>\n<li>Peak Power 1200w</li>\n<li>Deep smooth bass</li></ul><br>\n<p><b>6x9" Speakers Slick 693:</b></p>\n<ul><li>Tri-axial speaker (3-way)</li>\n<li>RMS Power 160w</li>\n<li>Peak Power 475w</li>\n<li>Sensitivity 90db</li>\n<li>Requencey Response 55-25 Khz</li></ul>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>\n\n<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Support</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p></p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>\n\n<newtab>\n<tabname><center>More Images</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p></p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/slickpack2/', NULL, '', 61, '<br>\n<li>800W 4 channel Amplifier </li>\n<li>Subwoofer Enclosure SLR12</li>\n<li>6x9" Speakers Slick 693</li>\n<li>Tri-axial speaker (3-way)</li>\n', ''),
(1523, 1, 'CT24VW04 Volkswagen Golf Passat Touran Facia Plate', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p><b>Suitable For:</b></p><br>\n<ul><li>VW Passat 2004 >  </li>\n<li>VW Golf 2003 > Mk5  </li>\n<li>VW Touran 2002 >  </li>\n<li>No Removable pocket</li></ul><br>\n<p>This Connects2 facia Plate will allow an aftermarket fitment of an Alpine, Clarion, Kenwood, Pioneer or Single Din radio of your choice while keeping a good quality OEM finish. </p><br>\n<p>In some cases you may also need a different wiring connection, Steering control lead or an aerial adapter, which are all available in our listings. </p><br>\n<p>If you have any questions or need assistance please call us on 0208 2880181 or email us at info@safensound.co.uk \n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>\n\n<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Features</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><ul><li>Colour of Facia: black</li></ul>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>\n\n<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Support</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc">\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>\n\n<newtab>\n<tabname><center>More Images</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>Whilst we endeavour to supply you with the correct fascia for your vehicle, we have no doubt there will be some vehicles caught in change over years, so we thought it would be useful to include various images of the interiors to assist you in choosing the correct parts.</p><br>\n<p>So the only choice you have to make is whether this looks like your interior!</p><br>\n<p>\n<table align="center" cellspacing="5" cellpadding="0">\n<tr>\n<td>\n<a href="images/more images/vw golf 2005/correct dash golf.jpg" rel="lightbox[vw golf 2005]" title="Image 1 - correct dash golf">\n<img src="images/more images/vw golf 2005/correct dash golf.jpg" width="120px">\n</a>\n</td>\n<td>\n<a href="images/more images/vw golf 2005/correct dash passat.jpg" rel="lightbox[vw golf 2005]" title="Image 2 - correct dash passat">\n<img 