(680, 1, 'Vibe Flatlines 0 Gauge Red Power Cable', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>VIBE FLATLINES power cable has been developed to maximised voltage transfer from battery to amplifier - The cable has 2 main lines running side by side which are made up of fine copper strands - This design makes the cable flat allowing us to make very slim heavy duty power cable which is highly flexible easing installation into vehicles.</p><br>\n<p>Model: FLATLINES 0 PWR - 0 gauge red power cable</p><br>\n<p><b>Sold by the metre </b></p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 73, '<br>\n<li>Model: FLATLINES 0 PWR</li>\n<li>0 gauge red power cable</li>\n<li>Sold by the metre</li>\n', ''),
(681, 1, 'Vibe Flatlines 0 Gauge Black Power Cable', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>VIBE FLATLINES power cable has been developed to maximised voltage transfer from battery to amplifier - The cable has 2 main lines running side by side which are made up of fine copper strands - This design makes the cable flat allowing us to make very slim heavy duty power cable which is highly flexible easing installation into vehicles.</p><br>\n<p>Model: FLATLINES 0 GND - 0 gauge black power cable</p><br>\n<p><b>Sold by the metre</b> </p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 41, '<br>\n<li>Model: FLATLINES 0 GND</li>\n<li>0 gauge black power cable </li>\n<li>Sold by the metre</li>\n', ''),
(682, 1, 'Vibe Flatlines 14 Amp Remote 18 Cable', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>The VIBE FLATLINES remote 18 power cable has been developed to maximised voltage transfer between the remote turn on output of the source unit to the amplifier with absolute minimal voltage drop.</p><br>\n<p>With a current rating of 14 amps this cable can easily handle multiple amplifiers fed via a relay in high power systems. (only available in system kits, not sold separately) Features in all VIBE system kits.</p><br>\n<p><b>Sold in 5m Length</b></p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 37, '<br>\n<li>Model: FLATLINES REMOTE 18</li>\n<li>14 Amps Current Rating </li>\n<li>Sold in 5m Length</li>\n', ''),
(683, 1, 'Vibe Flatstereo 5m RCA Full Range Interconnect Cable', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>The VIBE FLATSTEREO RCA is an OFC high definition 54 interconnect  delivering the fullest signal possible from source to amplifier - the cable make up has been developed to run flat with left and right cables running parallel both with individual screening but sharing an outer FLAT jacket easing installation.</p><br>\n<p>Model: FLATSTEREOTM RCA 5m - 5 metre 54 interconnect </p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 36, '<br>\n<li>Model: FLATSTEREOTM RCA 5m</li>\n<li>5 metre 54 interconnect</li>\n<li>Individual screening</li>\n', ''),
(684, 1, 'Vibe Flatstereo 1m RCA Full Range Interconnect Cable', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>The VIBE FLATSTEREO RCA is an OFC high definition 54 interconnect  delivering the fullest signal possible from source to amplifier - the cable make up has been developed to run flat with left and right cables running parallel both with individual screening but sharing an outer FLAT jacket easing installation.</p><br>\n<p>Model: FLATSTEREOTM RCA 1m - 1 metre 54 interconnect </p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 30, '<br>\n<li>Model: FLATSTEREOTM RCA 1m</li>\n<li>1 metre 54 interconnect</li>\n<li>Individual screening</li>\n', ''),
(685, 1, 'Vibe Flatbass 1m RCA Bass Interconnect Cable', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>The VIBE FLATBASS interconnect has been specifically developed for use in BASS SYSTEMS - the cable make up has a unique super FLAT design easing installation - Its trick ingredient is oversized SolidCore OFC signal wires - allowing a heavier voltage to be passed down the cable. This is the central wire that caries the main signal from source to amplifier.</p><br>\n<p>Model: FLATBASSTM RCA 1m  1 metre BASS interconnect</p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 386, '<br>\n<li>Model: FLATBASSTM RCA 1m</li>\n<li>1 metre bass interconnect</li>\n<li>Flat design</li>\n', ''),
(686, 1, 'Vibe Flatbass 5m RCA Bass Interconnect Cable', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>The VIBE FLATBASS interconnect has been specifically developed for use in BASS SYSTEMS - the cable make up has a unique super FLAT design easing installation - Its trick ingredient is oversized SolidCore OFC signal wires - allowing a heavier voltage to be passed down the cable. This is the central wire that caries the main signal from source to amplifier.</p><br>\n<p>Model: FLATBASSTM RCA 5m  5 metre BASS interconnect</p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 355, '<br>\n<li>Model: FLATBASSTM RCA 5m</li>\n<li>5 metre bass interconnect</li>\n<li>Flat design</li>\n', ''),
(687, 1, 'Vibe Flatflex 16 Gauge High Definition Flat Speaker cable', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>FLAT Multi-Strand OFC Speaker Cable</p><br>\n<p>Vibe high quality Multi-strand 54 cable with FLAT design for easy installation.</p><br>\n<p>Ideal for component or coaxial speaker systems - Maintain Perfect Clarity with FLAT16! </p><br>\n<p><b>Sold by the metre</b></p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 53, '<br>\n<li>Model: FlatFlexTM 16 SPK</li>\n<li>Maintain Perfect Clarity</li>\n<li>Sold by the metre</li>\n', ''),
(688, 1, 'Vibe Flatbass 13 Flat Solid Core OFC Subwoofer Cable', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>FLAT Solid Core OFC Subwoofer Cable</p><br>\n<p>Vibe Dedicated Flat Bass Cable, Perfect For Bass Boxes</p><br>\n<p>Flat cable for easy installation featuring massive solid cores for high power bass signals - Transfer all all of the bass from the amplifier to the subwoofer with FLAT13</p><br>\n<p><b>Sold by the metre</b></p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>\n\n<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Features</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p></p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>\n\n<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Support</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p></p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>\n\n<newtab>\n<tabname><center>More Images</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p></p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 48, '<br>\n<li>Model: FlatBass 13 SPK</li>\n<li>Flat cable for easy installation</li>\n<li>Sold by the metre</li>\n', ''),
(689, 1, 'Vibe FDAGU-V1 AGU Fuse Holder', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>Vibe Water proof Fuse holder to be located 12 approx from battery, holds glass type AGU fuses and offers reliable system protection. </p><br>\n<p>(AGU fuses available separately). </p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'http://www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 367, '<br>\n<li>Water proof Fuse holder</li>\n<li>Holds glass type AGU fuses</li>\n<li>Offers reliable system protection</li>\n', ''),
(690, 1, 'Vibe CB140 140 Amp Circuit Breaker', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>Big systems require big protection  The VIBE circuit breaker is rated at a massive 140 amps and offers critical protection to your system  if the system over powers or short circuits the breaker will cut in and save your equipment. No need to replace expensive fuses, the system is reset via a simple switch  also offers safe and instant system shutdown. </p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 368, '<br>\n<li>Rated at 140 amps</li>\n<li>Reset via a simple switch</li>\n<li>Offers reliable system protection</li>\n', ''),
(691, 1, 'Vibe FLAT Y 2F 2m RCA Y Lead 1 Male to 2 Female', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>Vibes professional quality 54 OFC Y-interconnect guarantees a pure and strong signal. With a flat design and ferrite loaded gold plated plugs interference is greatly reduced. The FLAT-Y Interconnect is available in 1 male  2 female FLAT Y 2F and 2 male  1 female FLAT Y 2M configurations.</p><br>\n<p>Model: FLAT Y 2F  RCA Y lead - 1 male to 2 female\n(n.b - 2xmale to 1xfemale model shown) </p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 53, '<br>\n<li>Quality 54 OFC Y-interconnect</li>\n<li>Guarantees a pure and strong signal</li>\n<li>Flat design</li>\n', ''),
(693, 1, 'Vibe GB41 Pair of Gold Banana Plugs', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>The VIBE GB41 banana plugs are the easy and convenient way to quickly remove your bass enclosure without having to constantly re-thread your speaker cable into the box terminal, simply attach the speaker cable to the VIBE GB41 banana plug and you have a fast easy reliable quick release solution. Designed for optimum use with the TP-2 and QP-4 terminal, Vibes professional gold plated 4mm banana plugs are polarity marked with rubber shrouds.</p><br>\n<p>Model: GB41  Gold banana plugs</p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 51, '<br>\n<li>Model: GB41</li>\n<li>Gold plated 4mm banana plugs</li>\n<li>Guarantees a pure and strong signal</li>\n', ''),
(692, 1, 'Vibe FLAT Y 2M RCA Y Lead 2 Male to 1 Female', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>Vibes professional quality 54 OFC Y-interconnect guarantees a pure and strong signal. With a flat design and ferrite loaded gold plated plugs interference is greatly reduced. The FLAT-Y Interconnect is available in 1 male  2 female FLAT Y 2F and 2 male  1 female FLAT Y 2M configurations.</p><br>\n<p>Model: FLAT Y 2F  RCA Y lead - 1 male to 2 female\n(n.b - 2xmale to 1xfemale model shown) </p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 55, '<br>\n<li>Quality 54 OFC Y-interconnect</li>\n<li>Guarantees a pure and strong signal</li>\n<li>Flat design</li>\n', ''),
(694, 1, 'Vibe DB6 6 Way Non Fused Distribution Block', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>The VIBE DB6 non fused block is a professional non fused block which gives easy connection for up to 5 amplifiers. The VIBE DB6 has 2 x 4AWG input and 4 x 8AWG outputs which can be used for power distribution or ground distribution giving a common grounding point for all system components eliminating the risk of ground loop interference.</p><br>\n<p>Model: DB6 non fused block</p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 75, '<br>\n<li>Model: DB6</li>\n<li>2 x 4AWG Inputs</li>\n<li>4 x 8AWG outputs</li>\n', ''),
(695, 1, 'Vibe FD4 Fused Distribution Block', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>The VIBE FD4 77 block is a professional AGU 77 block which gives easy connection for up to 4 amplifiers. The VIBE FD4 has 1 x 4AWG input and 4 x 8AWG outputs each individually fused up to a maximum of 80 amps (AGU fuses available separately)</p><br>\n<p>Model: FD4  4 way AGU 77 block, 1 x 4gauge input 4 x 8gauge outputs</p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 431, '<br>\n<li>Model: FD4</li>\n<li>1 x 4AWG input</li>\n<li>4 x 8AWG outputs</li>\n', ''),
(696, 1, 'Vibe CT0 0 Gauge Compression Fit Ring Terminal', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>The VIBE CT range of gold plated ring terminals are professional compression fit designed for maximum conductivity when connecting power cable to the vehicle battery. The VIBE RT compression fit terminals are the best way to connect heavy gauge power cable to the vehicles battery.</p><br>\n<p>Model: CT0  0 gauge compression fit ring terminal </p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 61, '<br>\n<li>Model: CT0</li>\n<li>Gold plated ring terminals </li>\n<li>Maximum conductivity</li>\n', ''),
(698, 1, 'Vibe CT4 4 Gauge Compression Fit Ring Terminal', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>The VIBE CT range of gold plated ring terminals are professional compression fit designed for maximum conductivity when connecting power cable to the vehicle battery. The VIBE RT compression fit terminals are the best way to connect heavy gauge power cable to the vehicles battery.</p><br>\n<p>Model: CT4  4 gauge compression fit ring terminal </p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 69, '<br>\n<li>Model: CT4</li>\n<li>Gold plated ring terminals </li>\n<li>Maximum conductivity</li>\n', ''),
(699, 1, 'Vibe RT4 Professional 4 Gauge Ring Terminals', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>The professional range of VIBE RT ring terminals for connecting power cable to the vehicle battery. Packed in pairs and include red and black rubber over boots and easy crimp design.</p><br>\n<p>Model: RT4  1 pair of 4 gauge crimp on ring terminals with PVC overboots </p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 62, '<br>\n<li>Model: RT4</li>\n<li>Red and black rubber over boots</li>\n<li>Easy crimp design</li>\n', ''),
(700, 1, 'Vibe RT8 8 Gauge Professional Ring Terminals', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>The professional range of VIBE RT ring terminals for connecting power cable to the vehicle battery. Packed in pairs and include red and black rubber over boots and easy crimp design.</p><br>\n<p>Model: RT8  1 pair of 8 gauge crimp on ring terminals with PVC overboots </p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 53, '<br>\n<li>Model: RT8</li>\n<li>Red and black rubber over boots</li>\n<li>Easy crimp design</li>\n', ''),
(701, 1, 'Vibe AGU30 Pair of Glass Fuses for AGU Fuse Holders', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>The VIBE AGU fuse series are the perfect companion to the VIBE FD4 distribution block and the Active and stereo system wiring kits. The VIBE AGU fuses are packed in pairs so you always have a spare fuse when you need one and are available in 30, 60 and 80 amp versions.</p><br>\n<p>Model: AGU30  1 pair 30 amp AGU fuses to fit all AGU 80</p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/cables/', NULL, '', 59, '<br>\n<li>Model: AGU30</li>\n<li>Packed in pairs</li>\n<li>30 amp AGU fuses</li>\n', ''),
