(1520, 1, 'Vibe CBR 15 Active 3200 Watt 15" Active Subwoofer', '<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>Re-designed and updatedthe new CBR Active range is the ultimate solution for your in car bass requirements. The active enclosure is made up of 3 perfectly matched components  1. the enclosure, the subwoofer and the amplifier .The tuned trinity components are so precisely matched they remain almost indestructible whilst at the same time balanced to offer uncompromised bass output.</p><br>\n<p>The active is a complete unit, all it requires is power and connection to your stereo. When combined with the VIBE FastPlug it makes for a very effective portable system, bass box out, shopping bags in!</p><br>\n<p>All new VIBE Blackair subwoofer loaded bass enclosure exclusive on active enclosures only. Retuned enclosure offering increased low bass performance and variable port tuning with 25mm and 18mm MDF construction, glued, screwed and braced for absolute rigidity.</p><br>\n<p>The VIBE PressureWedgeTM enclosure design creates internal pressures to assist cone control and enhance enclosure porting. The VIBE R&D have created the brand new and patented A.R.B.S.S anti resonance supportsystem which eliminates unwanted vibration for more defined bass whilst the flared VIBE TurboportTM eliminates unwanted port noise.</p><br>\n<p>The VIBE PortplugTM included which when inserted into the VIBE turboport tm seals the port making an airtight sealed enclosure offering different sound characteristics and the trademark VIBE crackle effect is applied through the new VIBE RubberCrackle that wraps the whole enclosure in a highly durable finish and adding anti vibration properties.</p><br>\n<p>All CBR actives feature a perfectly matched Blackbox integrated bass amplifier .\n</p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>\n\n<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Features</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><ul><li>Vibe CBR-15 Evo Active 3200 watt 15"active subwoofer </li>\n<li>Mega Deep Punch </li>\n<li>BlackBox Bass II Active Amp </li>\n<li>Wiring Kit Included </li>\n<li>Height 420 mm </li>\n<li>Width 590 mm </li>\n<li>Depth 455mm </li>\n<li>RMS Power 1100 watts </li>\n<li>Turbo Ports 2 x 4" </li></ul>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>\n\n<newtab>\n<tabname><center>Support</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p></p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>\n\n<newtab>\n<tabname><center>More Images</center></tabname>\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p></p>\n</div>\n</tabtext>\n</newtab>', 'www.vibeaudio.co.uk/products/blackaircbr15/', NULL, '', 56, '<br>\n<li>BlackBox Bass II Active Amp </li>\n<li>Wiring Kit Included </li>\n<li>RMS Power 1100 watts </li>\n<li>Turbo Ports 2 x 4" </li>\n', ''),
