(2300, 1, 'Alpine UTE-72BT Mechless unit with Bluetooth', '<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>The new Alpine Digital Media Receivers are better than ever. The Alpine UTE-72BT will let you make the most of your iPhone and iPod, and will also play back music files from a USB stick. </p><br>\r\n<p>Plus, the UTE-72BT is Bluetooth enabled for hands-free calling and music streaming. </p><br>\r\n<p>The Alpine UTE-72BT is a fantastic solution for enjoying your iPhone in your car, and much more. Featuring USB connection and full iPod compatibility, the UTE-72BT gives you seamless control over your music sources.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Features</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p><b>Key Features </b></p><br>\r\n<ul><li>FM Presets: 18. MW: 6, LW: 6 </li>\r\n<li>RDS tuner with auto-memory, TA, AF, EON, Radio Text </li>\r\n<li>Integrated Bluetooth module with Microphone included </li>\r\n<li>Works with Nokia (requires KCU-230NK) </li>\r\n<li>Made for iPhone and iPod (KCU-445i required - same as standard iPod USB lead) </li>\r\n<li>Front USB port with 1A charging power </li></ul><br>\r\n<p><b>General Features </b></p><br>\r\n<ul><li>App Direct Mode for control using the portable device </li>\r\n<li>AUX input on the front panel (3.5mm jack) </li>\r\n<li>Detachable Control Panel with Case </li>\r\n<li>Button Illumination: red </li>\r\n<li>Menu language can be changed in 7 languages </li>\r\n<li>Suitable for steering wheel control </li>\r\n<li>Remote Control RUE-4202 available as an optional accessory </li>\r\n<li>White LCD display in dot matrix design </li>\r\n<li>Dimmer function </li></ul><br>\r\n<p><b>Bluetooth Features </b></p><br>\r\n<ul><li>Streaming audio with A2DP with AVRCP control (BT V3.0) </li>\r\n<li>Simple Secure Pairing (no code required) </li>\r\n<li>Up to five phones can be coupled (1,000 numbers per phone) </li>\r\n<li>Six individually adjustable speed dial numbers </li>\r\n<li>Indication of the GSM signal strength and battery level </li>\r\n<li>Icon in SMS inbox </li>\r\n<li>Call Waiting </li>\r\n<li>Ringer, microphone and volume control </li>\r\n<li>Alphabetical name search (Search ABC)</li></ul> </p><br>\r\n<p><b>Audio Features </b></p><br>\r\n<ul><li>Maximum power output 4 x 50W </li>\r\n<li>2 pre-outs (2 Volts) </li>\r\n<li>Bass Engine Pro 3-band parametric EQ (+/-7dB) </li>\r\n<li>MediaXpander </li>\r\n<li>Volume control of each source (+ /-14dB) </li>\r\n<li>10 pre-installed sound settings </li>\r\n<li>High Pass Filter (Front/Rear) and low-pass filter (subwoofer) </li>\r\n<li>Subwoofer level (0-15dB) and phasing (0/180) </li></ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Support</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc">\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>More Images</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc">\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>', '', '<a target="_blank" href="http://rover.ebay.com/rover/1/710-53481-19255-0/1?icep_ff3=9&pub=5575070011&toolid=10001&campid=5337588014&customid=&icep_uq=ute-72bt&icep_sellerId=&icep_ex_kw=&icep_sortBy=12&icep_catId=&icep_minPrice=&icep_maxPrice=&ipn=psmain&icep_vectorid=229508&kwid=902099&mtid=824&kw=lg">&lt;img src=&quot;catalog/images/buttons/ebay_compare.png&quot; style=&quot;border-style: none;&quot;&gt;</a><img style="text-decoration:none;border:0;padding:0;margin:0;" src="http://rover.ebay.com/roverimp/1/710-53481-19255-0/1?ff3=9&pub=5575070011&toolid=10001&campid=5337588014&customid=&uq=ute-72bt&mpt=[CACHEBUSTER]">', '', 1621, '<br><li>Integrated Bluetooth Mic included </li>\r\n<li>Works with Nokia (requires KCU-230NK) </li>\r\n<li>App Direct Mode</li>', ''),
(2227, 1, 'Connects2 CTKBM04 BMW 5 Series E39 For Pioneer', '<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>When replacing your factory fit radio with an aftermarket Pioneer unit you will probably require one of our specialist kits. </p><br>\r\n<p>Suitable for the following vehicle: </p><br>\r\n<ul><li>BMW 5 Series E39 1995 - 2004</li></ul><br>\r\n<p><b>Please Note: We advise to use Double Din stereos without a motorised front panel.</b></p><br>\r\n<p>This Connects2 CTKBM04 kit will supply you with everything needed to complete your installation, including Double Din Facia and Steering Wheel Interface.</p><br>\r\n<p>Some companies will charge you for a seperate Pioneer patch lead for this kit to work.</p><br>\r\n<p>We will include this lead <b>FREE</b> of charge with your order.</p><br>\r\n<p><b>We offer an installation service on all products. Please call 0208 2880181 for more info.</b></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Features</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p><b>Installation Kit Contains:</b></p><br>\r\n<ul><li>CT23BM04 - Double DIN Fascia </li>\r\n<li>CTSBM003 and CTSBM004 - Steering Control Interfaces With Wiring looms for Flat and round pin vehicles (saves having to guess what type you have) </li>\r\n<li>CT27AA06 - Antenna adaptor </li></ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Support</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc">\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>More Images</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc">\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>', '', NULL, '', 1283, '<br><li>CT23BM04 - Double DIN Fascia </li>\r\n<li>CTSBM003 and CTSBM004 - Steering Control Interfaces With Wiring looms for Flat and round pin vehicles (saves having to guess what type you have) </li>\r\n<li>CT27AA06 - Antenna adaptor </li>', ''),
(2293, 1, 'DNX-4210DAB - Double Din DVD/USB/Bluetooth & DAB', '<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p><b>KENWOOD''S FIRST MULTIMEDIA SYSTEM WITH DAB TECHNOLOGY</b></p><br>\r\n<p>Introducing the first multimedia system from Kenwood Electronics featuring cutting-edge digital radio technology. The all-new DNX4210DAB offers playback of hundreds of radio stations at the touch of a button. At last there is a station for all tastes --Sport -Jazz --rock even if youre a child of the 60/70/80ties there is a home for you ! The easy-search system makes finding the right station quick, and once tuned in the latest technology means that listening to digital radio on the move is free of annoying breaks and distortion. iPod hook-up, full European navigation, seamless Bluetooth mobile phone integration and DVD-playback all brought to you via touch-screen technology and a super-fast Central Processor Unit make this the ultimate multimedia system. With the Kenwood DNX4210DAB, you can get your favourite FM/AM stations on digital , as well as lots of digital-only stations. Digital radio has something for everyone.</p><br>\r\n<p><b>New App Feature:</b></p><br>\r\n<p>New for 2012 - iPod/iPhone App Control Mode*. This feature enables you to operate compatible apps such as YouTube, iTunes U and also allows you to view your own videos which are on your iPod/iPhone. *App dependent on "external control license.</p><br>\r\n<p><b>KEY FEATURES </b></p><br>\r\n<ul><li>6.1 wide VGA touch screen</li>\r\n<li>2D animated graphical user interface</li>\r\n<li>DAB tuner built-in</li>\r\n<li>Multilanguage text & tag display</li>\r\n<li>CD/DVD/USB/player, iPod ready</li>\r\n<li>Navigation system built-in, powered by Garmin</li>\r\n<li>Bluetooth handsfree built-in (powered by Telechips)</li>\r\n<li>GUI with selectable 20 languages menu & text display</li>\r\n<li>Audio & video playback from USB/DVD/USB/SD/iPod</li>\r\n<li>AV-in, AV-out & Rear camera inpu