(1746, 1, 'Pioneer TS-Q171C Citroen / Peugeot 2-Way Speaker System', '<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>Citroen and Peugeot drivers these are the speakers designed exclusively for your car! Custom-tuned and designed, the TS-Q171C component speakers offer an easy, one-stop solution for upgrading the factory-fitted system.</p><br>\r\n<p>The 17cm KEVLAR composite cone woofer and 25mm soft dome tweeter deliver a better and more impressive sound offering throughout the 54. Where the woofer guarantees a lively dimension, the Soft Dome tweeter adds natural overtones. In short, a smooth and accurate audio experience.</p><br>\r\n<p>The front-mounted magnetic circuit of the TS-Q171C allows for a perfect fit and easy installation, helped by the clear and simple installation guide included in the package.\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Features</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p><b>Specification </b></p><br>\r\n<ul><li>Frequency response: 35 - 28.000 Hz </li>\r\n<li>Sensitivity (1W/1m): 89 dB </li>\r\n<li>Maximum Power: 220 Watt </li>\r\n<li>Nominal input power: 40 Watt </li>\r\n<li>Woofer size (cm): 17 cm </li>\r\n<li>Woofer material: KEVLAR brand composite cone woofer with butyl rubber edge </li>\r\n<li>Tweeter size (mm): 25,0 mm </li>\r\n<li>Tweeter material: Soft dome tweeter with Neodymium Magnet </li></ul><br>\r\n<p><b>Comaptible Vehicles:</b></p><br>\r\n<ul><li>Citroen: C2, C3, C3 Pluriel, C4, C5, C8, Xsar Picasso, Xsara, Evasion, Berlingo </li>\r\n<li>Peugeot: 206, 307, 406, 406 Coupe, 407, 407 Coupe, 607, 806, 807, 1007, Partner</li></ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Support</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc">\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>More Images</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc">\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>', '', NULL, '