(2279, 1, 'Dension Gateway 500S BT iPod/iPhone kit with Bluetooth', '<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p><b>Gateway 500S BT</b> is Dension''s premium interface and is designed to work with cars which utilize the fiber optic MOST system. As with other Gateways, it works by emulating the CD changer (in most cases) in the vehicle and enables you to use the original radio controls.</p><br>\r\n<p><b>If the car has a CD changer fitted, then Gateway 500 will integrate automatically.</b></p><br>\r\n<p><b>If not, the CDC function may have to be enabled/programmed.</b></p><br>\r\n<p><b>The car configuration (compatibility) is set using dip switches according to the car brand.</b></p><br>\r\n<p><b>Supported USB devices:</b></p><br>\r\n<ul><li>USB: Flash Memory and Hard Disk Drive (UBS1.1 and higher)</li>\r\n<li>File System: FAT16 or FAT32</li>\r\n<li>Storage capacity: up to 320GB music content</li>\r\n<li>Music Format: MP3, WMA and WAV,</li>\r\n<li>OGG</li></ul><br>\r\n<p><b>Supported iPod / iPhone devices:</b></p><br>\r\n<ul><li>iPod Classic</li>\r\n<li>iPod (4th generation)</li>\r\n<li>iPod nano (1st, 2nd, 3rd, 4th, 5th and 6th generation)</li>\r\n<li>iPod mini</li>\r\n<li>iPod Photo 4G</li>\r\n<li>iPod Video 5G</li>\r\n<li>iPod touch (1st, 2nd, 3rd and 4th gen.)</li>\r\n<li>iPhone, iPhone 4S / 4 and 3GS / 3G</li></ul><br>\r\n<p><b>Gateway 500S BT covers most compatibility of the previous Gateway 500 (GW51MO2).</b></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Features</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><ul><li>All in ONE device : Bluetooth handsfree, full iPod/iPhone control, USB playback</li>\r\n<li>1A charging is supported (no Power Booster is needed)</li>\r\n<li>Song information and browsing on vehicle screen (ID3-Tag)</li>\r\n<li>A2DP audio streaming</li>\r\n<li>3,5 mm Aux-in</li>\r\n<li>Control via original  car audio system controls (including steering wheel controls  if available)</li>\r\n<li>Retain the original dashboard aesthetic</li>\r\n<li>Both single and dual FOT versions are available</li>\r\n</ul><br>\r\n<p><b>Integrated Bluetooth</b></p><br>\r\n<p>In addition to iPod and USB music playback, both the single and dual FOT versions of Gateway 500S BT includes Bluetooth. Not only does this enable hands free telephone operations but also allows A2DP music streaming to the original car audio system.</p><br>\r\n<ul><li>Make and receive hands free calls in the car</li>\r\n<li>Browse phone book on the car''s original screen(s)</li>\r\n<li>Phone audio through car speakers</li>\r\n<li>Stream music from your phone to the car audio system</li>\r\n<li>Use original controls</li></ul><br>\r\n<p><b>Package content:</b></p><br>\r\n<ul><li>Hardware</li>\r\n<li>Optical harness</li>\r\n<li>Power cable</li>\r\n<li>iPod Dock Cable</li>\r\n<li>Microphone</li>\r\n<li>Installation and user guide</li></ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Support</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><a href="http://www.dension.com/sites/default/files/gateway-500s-with-bt-gw52xxx/en/user-guide/gateway500s_install_guide.pdf" target="_blank"><img src="images/icons/pdf.png" align="left" style="vertical-align:middle"/>Instruction Manual</a><br>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.dension.com/sites/default/files/gateway-500s-with-bt-gw52xxx/en/user-guide/gateway500s_user_manual.pdf" target="_blank"><img src="images/icons/pdf.png" align="left" style="vertical-align:middle"/>Instruction Manual</a><br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>BMW vehicle compatibility:</b><br><br>\r\n<a href=javascript:popUp(''http://www.dension.com/sites/default/files/car-compatibility/bmw_12_07_12.pdf'',''window'',''400'',''500'')><img src="images/icons/car.png" align="left" style="vertical-align:middle" />Compatible Vehicles</a><br>\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>More Images</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p><table align="center" cellspacing="5" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<a href="catalog/images/more images/gateway 500s/6052.jpg" rel="lightbox[gateway 500s]" title="Image 1 - 6052">\r\n<img src="catalog/images/more images/gateway 500s/6052.jpg" width="120px">\r\n</a>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<a href="catalog/images/more images/gateway 500s/6059.jpg" rel="lightbox[gateway 500s]" title="Image 2 - 6059">\r\n<img src="catalog/images/more images/gateway 500s/6059.jpg" width="120px">\r\n</a>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<a href="catalog/images/more images/gateway 500s/6061.jpg" rel="lightbox[gateway 500s]" title="Image 3 - 6061">\r\n<img src="catalog/images/more images/gateway 500s/6061.jpg" width="120px">\r\n</a>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<a href="catalog/images/more images/gateway 500s/gateway500s-bt.jpg" rel="lightbox[gateway 500s]" title="Image 4 - gateway500s-bt">\r\n<img src="catalog/images/more images/gateway 500s/gateway500s-bt.jpg" width="120px">\r\n</a>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>', '', NULL, '', 902, '<li>Integrated Bluetooth</li>\r\n<li>A2DP audio streaming</li>\r\n<li>iPhone, ipod compatable</li>\r\n<li>3.5 mm Aux-in</li>\r\n<li>Retain the original dashboard aesthetic</li>', ''),
(2286, 1, 'Focal K2 Power 165 KR component speakers', '<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>Focal K2 Power 165KR 16.5cm 2-way component speakers\r\nAt Focal, all that matters is music. Focal''s sound gurus engage in intensive listening sessions as they design a new line of speakers, making it their mission to create products that deliver uncanny realism, sweeping dynamics, and breathtaking depth. During the hands-on production process, they test every model meticulously to ensure that they meet Focal''s exacting standards. </p><br>\r\n<p>Focal''s "Power Hi-Fi" philosophy\r\nThe K2 Power 165KR 6-1/2" component speaker system bears the hallmarks of Focal''s "Power Hi-Fi" philosophy. The nimble Aramid and glass-fiber woofers demonstrate the control needed to reproduce delicate classical passages, yet they''ll handle the power needed to drive your bass-heavy music with authority. The sturdy zinc-aluminum alloy baskets are non-magnetic so they won''t interfere with the speaker''s own electronics. </p><br>\r\n<p>Inverted dome tweeter design\r\nFocal''s inverted dome tweeters act like little woofers, dispersing the highs in a wide pattern to create an exceptionally natural soundstage. K2 Power crossovers use hand-made components developed by Focal to deliver an ideal blend of the highs and lows for a dynamic stereo image. Three levels of tweeter and two levels of midrange control let you dial in the sound to your car''s environment.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Features</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><ul><li>component speaker system includes two 6-1/2" woofers, 2 tweeters, 2 external crossovers, and 2 woofer grilles</li>\r\n<li>K2 composite woofer cone (Aramid, foam, and glass fiber)</li>\r\n<li>butyl rubber surround</li>\r\n<li>1-3/4" woven Aramid fiber inverted-dome tweeter</li>\r\n<li>2-way external crossover with 3 tweeter and 2 midrange level settings</li>\r\n<li>4-ohm impedance</li>\r\n<li>power range: 6-80 watts RMS (160 watts peak power)</li>\r\n<li>frequency response: 60-20,000 Hz</li>\r\n<li>sensitivity: 91 dB @ 2.83 V</li>\r\n<li>mounting depth: 2-13/16"</li>\r\n<li>warranty: 1 year</li></ul><br>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.focal.com/files/fp-165-kr.pdf" target="_blank"><img src="images/icons/pdf.png" align="left" style="vertical-align:middle"/>Instruction Manual</a><br></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Support</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p><a href="http://www.focal.com/files/notice-kit-k2-power.pdf" target="_blank"><img src="images/icons/pdf.png" align="left" style="vertical-align:middle"/>User Guide</a><br></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>More Images</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p><table align="center" cellspacing="5" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<a href="catalog/images/more images/focal 165kr/foc 165kr.jpg" rel="lightbox[focal 165kr]" title="Image 1 - foc 165kr">\r\n<img src="catalog/images/more images/focal 165kr/foc 165kr.jpg" width="120px">\r\n</a>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<a href="catalog/images/more images/focal 165kr/focal 165 kr.jpg" rel="lightbox[focal 165kr]" title="Image 2 - focal 165 kr">\r\n<img src="catalog/images/more images/focal 165kr/focal 165 kr.jpg" width="120px">\r\n</a>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<a href="catalog/images/more images/focal 165kr/power 165kr.jpg" rel="lightbox[focal 165kr]" title="Image 3 - power 165kr">\r\n<img src="catalog/images/more images/focal 165kr/power 165kr.jpg" width="120px">\r\n</a>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>', 'www.focal.com/en/car-audio-sound/haut-parleurs/kits-2-voies-se-pare-es/165-kr.php', NULL, '', 1035, '<br><li>K2 composite woofer cone (Aramid, foam, and glass fiber)</li>\r\n<li>butyl rubber surround</li>\r\n<li>1-3/4" woven Aramid fiber inverted-dome tweeter</li>\r\n<li>4-ohm impedance</li>\r\n<li>6-80 watts RMS (160 watts peak power)</li>', ''),
