(2174, 1, 'Vibe BlackAir 5 v2 5" Component Speakers', '<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>The all new BlackAir 5 speakers represent the pinnacle of in car entertainment speaker performance. </p><br>\r\n<p>The BlackAir 5 speaker is engineered such as to get perfect integration between the woofer and the tweeter. The woofer using a Honeycomb fibreglass cone combined with a polyurethane surround gives a sharp, precise and reference quality sound. The BlackAir range is an extremely musical speaker and unfailingly accurate in their performance. The silk dome tweeter is engineered such that it can keep up with and match the woofer perfectly and inherently with this has a very high power handling. </p><br>\r\n<p>The BlackAir components make your installation choices incredibly versatile, the tweeter comes with a multitude of installation choices including surface and flush mountings. These speakers deliver reference quality sound helping you to produce razor sharp detail within your system. They provide exceptional sound delivered without any limitations. The Vibe BlackAir is the studio speaker designed for the car.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Features</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><ul><li>Ultra high quality woven Honeycomb fibreglass cone </li>\r\n<li>Multi-Installation options </li>\r\n<li>Tweeters can be used in a surface or flush mount applications </li>\r\n<li>High powered woofer and tweeter engineered to work harmony </li>\r\n<li>SPEEDBASS Polyurethane surround keeps the bass fast </li>\r\n<li>New VIBE angular torsion alloy cast basket </li>\r\n<li>2 way 12 dB per octave passive crossover </li>\r\n<li>5" (130mm) </li>\r\n<li>100w RMS Power Handling </li>\r\n<li>300w Max Power Handling </li>\r\n<li>90dB Sensitivity </li>\r\n<li>Frequency Response 60 - 25,000Hz </li>\r\n<li>4ohm </li>\r\n<li>Mounting Depth 60mm</li></ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Support</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc">\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>More Images</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc">\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>', '', NULL, '', 512, '<br>\r\n<li>5" (130mm) </li>\r\n<li>100w RMS Power Handling </li>\r\n<li>300w Max Power Handling </li>\r\n<li>90dB Sensitivity </li>', ''),
(2175, 1, 'Vibe BlackAir 6 v2 6" Component Speakers', '<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>Vibe BlackAir 6 The all new Vibe BlackAir speakers represent the pinnacle of in car entertainment speaker performance. </p><br>\r\n<p>The speaker is engineered such as to get perfect integration between the woofer and the tweeter. The woofer using a Honeycomb fibreglass cone combined with a polyurethane surround gives a sharp, precise and reference quality sound. The BlackAir range is an extremely musical speaker and unfailingly accurate in their performance. The silk dome tweeter is engineered such that it can keep up with and match the woofer perfectly and inherently with this has a very high power handling. </p><br>\r\n<p>The BlackAir components make your installation choices incredibly versatile, the tweeter comes with a multitude of installation choices including surface and flush mountings. These speakers deliver reference quality sound helping you to produce razor sharp detail within your system. They provide exceptional sound delivered without any limitations. The Vibe BlackAir is the studio speaker designed for the car.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Features</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><ul><li>Ultra high quality woven Honeycomb fibreglass cone </li>\r\n<li>Multi-Installation options </li>\r\n<li>Tweeters can be used in a surface or flush mount applications </li>\r\n<li>High powered woofer and tweeter engineered to work harmony </li>\r\n<li>SPEEDBASS Polyurethane surround keeps the bass fast </li>\r\n<li>New VIBE angular torsion alloy cast basket </li>\r\n<li>2 way 12 dB per octave passive crossover </li>\r\n<li>6.25" (165mm) </li>\r\n<li>120w RMS Power Handling </li>\r\n<li>360w Max Power Handling </li>\r\n<li>90dB Sensitivity </li>\r\n<li>Frequency Response 60 - 25,000Hz </li>\r\n<li>4ohm </li>\r\n<li>Mounting Depth 62mm</li></ul>\r\n</div>\r