(2320, 1, 'Pioneer AVIC-F960DAB High-end CD,DVD, GPS Navigation', '<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Description</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc"><p>All-in-one car entertainment and navigation.</p><br>\r\n<p>This multimedia NavGate system combines high quality audio and video with smart navigation. Keep all your passengers happy and connect your smartphone with app radio mode or MirrorLink and stream whatever they feel like watching or listening to. The AVICSYNC app lets you access connected services such as traffic, weather and more. Youll benefit from fresh map data and the most up-to-date and current information.</p><br>\r\n<p>The AVIC-F960DABs large 6.1&#8243; multi-touch display is designed to look the part with its new and improved interface that runs on Android OS. Similar to your smartphone it is intuitive, easy to use, and it assures safer operation in your car.</p><br>\r\n<p>\r\nApple CarPlay</p><br>\r\n<p>The AVIC-F960DAB will be one of the first aftermarket radios to feature Apple CarPlay (firmware update required, coming summer 2014). CarPlay is the smarter, safer and more fun way to use your iPhone in the car. CarPlay gives iPhone users an incredibly intuitive way to make calls, use Maps, listen to music and access messages with just a word or a touch.\r\n Learn more at www.apple.com/ios/carplay</p><br>\r\n<p>\r\nMulti-touch, hi-res & capacitive display</p><br>\r\n<p>The buttons and high contrast, anti-glare screen can be adapted to your taste. You can also enjoy an optimised multi-touch response.</p><br>\r\n<p>Improved connectivity</p><br>\r\n<p>Keep up-to-date and travel faster with AVICSYNC. Connect your smartphone to your NavGate system and enjoy location-based services, more road coverage, accuracy, map and software updates. The AVICSYNC smartphone app will be available by the end of this year.</p><br>\r\n<p>\r\nFor better sound</p><br>\r\n<p>Superior sound is guaranteed thanks to high-end audio components and the Digital Signal Processor, which calculates the perfect time alignment settings and has a sophisticated Auto EQ section.</p><br>\r\n<p>\r\nApps in your car</p><br>\r\n<p>Control compatible smartphone apps directly from your car dashboard via AppRadio Mode or MirrorLink.</p><br>\r\n<p>\r\nEats anything</p><br>\r\n<p>Connect any device to listen to your favourite songs or watch a movie via: CD, DVD, iPod, iPhone, USB, HDMI, SD, Aux-in, and Bluetooth.</p><br>\r\n<p>\r\nParrot Bluetooth module</p><br>\r\n<p>In addition to basic features such as hands-free calling and music audio streaming, this Bluetooth module includes: wide band speech for a clearer voice and enhanced voice recognition, and file browsing.</p><br>\r\n<p>\r\nAvoid traffic jams</p><br>\r\n<p>Get to your final destination faster thanks to these built-in traffic message services: TMC, ViaMichelin, Mediamobile Nordic, Inrix and pre-installed Here Maps.</p><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<p>Digital Audio Broadcasting</p><br>\r\n<p>Thanks to the integrated DAB-tuner you will be able to listen to your favourite radio stations in digital sound quality without distortion.</p><br>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Features</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc">\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>Support</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc">\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>\r\n\r\n<newtab>\r\n<tabname><center>More Images</center></tabname>\r\n<tabtext><div id="prodDesc">\r\n</div>\r\n</tabtext>\r\n</newtab>', '', '<a target="_blank" href="http://rover.ebay.com/rover/1/710-53481-19255-0/1?icep_ff3=9&pub=5575070011&toolid=10001&campid=5337621253&customid=&icep_uq=Pioneer+AVIC-F960DAB&icep_sellerId=&icep_ex_kw=&icep_sortBy=12&icep_catId=&icep_minPrice=&icep_maxPrice=&ipn=psmain&icep_vectorid=229508&kwid=902099&mtid=824&kw=lg">&lt;img src=&quot;catalog/images/buttons/ebay_compare.png&quot; style=&quot;border-style: none;&quot;&gt;</a><img style="text-decoration:none;border:0;padding:0;margin:0;" src="http://rover.ebay.com/roverimp/1/710-53481-19255-0/1?ff3=9&pub=5575070011&toolid=10001&campid=5337621253&customid=&uq=Pioneer+AVIC-F960DAB&mpt=[CACHEBUSTER]">', '', 308, '', '');
